{"tid":1488880,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[聚焦] 8月23號起仲有大把行動呀！","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:30:29.000Z","uid":39138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ad215f768e89ee0a448d01218ca079493cdcd7fb","tid":1488880,"uid":39138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"依家望到連登真係屌出黎<br />\n出面全部都係大波狗裸跑找數post同屌做咩follow大波狗同屌做咩裸跑post，每個topic開幾個post，將啲有用同行動post沉哂落底<br />\n我係對家真係笑左出黎，咁撚易就分化到<br />\n<br />\n你地咁互屌只會再引伸多更多同類型post，好似檢討日本民運失敗原因post又開多幾個<br />\n究竟你地目標係想互屌定係focus係黎緊既抗爭活動<br />\n你係要屌既唔該開返個 行動文宣標題，<br />\n屌完再宣傳返黎緊既行動，好過剩屌less productive，<br />\n我相信你只要有文宣絕對唔算標題黨<br />\n<br />\n麻煩咁多位手足focus返，唔好咁易俾人分化失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>823：香港之路（人鏈）<br />\n824：燃點香港 全民覺醒（觀塘區遊行）<br />\n825：荃葵青大遊行<br />\n<br />\n覺得文宣唔係好夠 希望大家推一推 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNVmQ0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNVmQ0H.jpg&h=2b8fc5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gq1tv0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGq1tv0J.jpg&h=bae4fcda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtnPZT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtnPZT3.jpg&h=12655e81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9aFm7o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9aFm7o.jpg&h=86a18c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/raMk6y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FraMk6y4.jpg&h=6889bdff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/